data.description: Welcome home to this impeccably maintained end unit townhome with main floor primary bedroom that is a perfect fit for anyone! The main floor has been thoughtfully renovated with brand-new luxury vinyl plank for easy maintenance. Your gourmet kitchen features a large center island with beautiful quartz countertops throughout, gas range/oven, separate pantry & open concept living looking into the dining and family room areas. The dining area has also been expanded to include a full coffee bar, reclaimed wood shelving and additional cabinetry complemented by the installation of all-new appliances. The family room is the perfect place to entertain and has enough room to really make it your own! Going down the hall you will find the primary bedroom with an en suite primary bathroom featuring a barn door entry and separate walk-in closet. Going through the barn door into your primary bath, you can enjoy two separate vanities and a spacious walk-in shower. Completing the main floor is a powder room & laundry area. Upstairs holds two more generous sized bedrooms with their own full bathroom. Bedroom #2 is oversized with large closet & views to the west and south. Bedroom #3 includes a large walk-in closet & views to the south.  This home is set up to be ADA adaptable on the main floor with oversized doorways, oversized shower in the primary suite, ramp to the front porch area and zero entry front door threshold. Don't wait, come and see this home today!
